des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your FOTILE range hood. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our "FOTILE connect" app in app market, then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in "FOTILE connect" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable "FOTILE connect" skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say "Search complete";
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the range hood.”
“Alexa, turn off the range hood.”
“Alexa, turn on the light.”
“Alexa, turn off the light.”
“Alexa, set the range hood to high speed.”
“Alexa, set the range hood to low speed.”
